              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "50",
                  "description": "Max number of customers to return. Optional. Default: 50. Min: 1. Max: 200."
                },
                {
                  "key": "offset",
                  "value": "0",
                  "description": "Number of customers to skip (0-based). Optional. Default: 0."
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Retrieves customers with offset pagination.\n\n**Query params**\n- `limit` (number, optional, default: `50`, max: `200`) — page size.\n- `offset` (number, optional, default: `0`) — number of records to skip.\n\n**Response**\n```json\n{\n  \"customers\": [/* Customer[] */],\n  \"limit\": 50,\n  \"offset\": 0\n}\n```"
